{"tid":2134970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［張馳有道？］支那旁邊只有香港、新疆兩個地方有疫情","createTime":"2020-08-01T06:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T17:24:01.000Z","uid":48124,"like":42,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"034181983dbac22680e705761e7cd57be2aec74f","tid":2134970,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:10:21.000Z","msg":"有否發覺，全支那旁邊只有兩個地方有疫情。<br />\n<br />\n新疆、香港。<br />\n<br />\n彷彿只要是不聽話的地方，便會有第二波第三波疫情一樣。<br />\n<br />\n中國在星期二、三，連續兩日破百確診，打破連續4個月未曾破百確診紀錄。巧合地，9成病例來自新疆。<br />\n<br />\n對病毒，可防可控，收放自如。<br />\n<br />\n追溯遠一點，去年11月區議會選舉，建制大敗，當時已有聲音，因應社運，醞釀延遲翌年9月立法會選舉。當然，因社運原因押後立會，代表政府示弱，原因站不住腳。巧合地，適逢武肺，劇本應運而生。<br />\n<br />\n還記得，香港2、3月的時候，每日4、5宗確診，已經煞有介事，全香港停工。<br />\n<br />\n你估，香港政府在2至5月期間，豁免檢疫逾20萬人入境，政府知唔知會有風險？<br />\n<br />\n還是只是有心人早已承受了風險，配合劇本，預見會有幾個、幾十個有病毒的人，差不多時間便會在社區跑跑跳跳，到處食飯搭的士呢？<br />\n<br />\n嗯，第三波了。彷彿過百宗確診也不痛不癢，遲遲不公佈WFH，讓病毒飛多一回，感染多一回，時間便剛剛好。<br />\n<br />\n結果，9月立會選舉，因應疫情，押後一年。<br />\n<br />\n一切好像跟著劇本去演一樣。押後選舉，只是其中一件要做的事。同時間，其他事情亦加速完成。<br />\n<br />\n巧合地，香港亞博變成了方艙醫院。<br />\n<br />\n巧合地，中國醫療隊，明日便有先遣隊7人到港進行實驗工作，其後可不斷增加來港人數。<br />\n<br />\n巧合地，全世界都在加速研發疫苗，研究時間差不多了，如果沒有確診，如何「集中營式」進行臨床實驗呢？<br />\n<br />\n說起劇本。<br />\n<br />\n2015年，廣州站發生新疆維吾爾人隨機狂斬13人，血洗車站。同年，新疆「再教育營」便出現了。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/108970510452155/posts/305426824139855/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F108970510452155%2Fposts%2F305426824139855%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=8d57556b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/108970510452155/posts/305426824139855/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n睇埋另一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英媒：中國以體檢名義採集新疆人DNA樣本<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/press-review-42340636\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fpress-review-42340636&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=9f3e08bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fpress-review-42340636&h=fc88ac89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/press-review-42340636</a>"},{"pid":"4993cda051566905122cce5369a168260e9a9cd8","tid":2134970,"uid":51469,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:11:43.000Z","msg":"大連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b468f0c05d71ecee277d5f6886a39c5d285a033a","tid":2134970,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:13:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b13dfd47df3c6e0f97755f70b45722a912764a6","tid":2134970,"uid":27530,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:14:27.000Z","msg":"北京咪之前爆過，垃圾文章"},{"pid":"d346dc51374624e0ebf1d7f700db41d6d967d8d2","tid":2134970,"uid":52658,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:14:46.000Z","msg":"台灣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea81048f7d9a364f19cad91350f43626616294e","tid":2134970,"uid":55533,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7b13dfd47df3c6e0f97755f70b45722a912764a6","tid":2134970,"uid":27530,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:14:27.000Z","msg":"北京咪之前爆過，垃圾文章"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T06:23:42.000Z","msg":"北京個啲好快無左啦<br />\n仲要好零星1，2宗<br />\n<br />\nbtw數字既野，至於你信不信，反正你信了"},{"pid":"2ecbe58c804651a5667fe34cd7813edc4fa1b494","tid":2134970,"uid":113155,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7b13dfd47df3c6e0f97755f70b45722a912764a6","tid":2134970,"uid":27530,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"cit